{"tid":1506121,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"開個跳閘哨兵 TG group ，有冇得諗？","createTime":"2019-08-25T17:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T17:18:25.000Z","uid":42943,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8eb77e15782d288bb28afd72a98d8c5920d5b6c5","tid":1506121,"uid":42943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:10:04.000Z","msg":"手足一齊留意邊度有查飛狗<br />\n大家可以安全啲抵制黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65328f6cea43a508aa09abc9c6b41da68278b233","tid":1506121,"uid":42943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:11:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"726d2ad78f24d1cc29d7dfdfc6a0178757b15233","tid":1506121,"uid":4458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:12:26.000Z","msg":"幫推 黨鐵正垃圾"},{"pid":"1d3b4d204e557bad43e43ec60fd910e359adabf2","tid":1506121,"uid":117968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:13:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4521b25ec39ed62faced5f2994d5cc9db1bd8d36","tid":1506121,"uid":42943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:13:15.000Z","msg":"幫手整個啦，我唔太識tg"},{"pid":"1e29be3bbb4bcdd2ccf261dd2f007ce02f606018","tid":1506121,"uid":227381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:13:34.000Z","msg":"可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96695dac52bcfeb5eb3e8e6be86cc381f459091","tid":1506121,"uid":206812,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:13:42.000Z","msg":"家母一路睇電視 見好多人爬山嘅時候<br />\n俾狗咬住個背囊走唔甩 咬到好傷好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以用師奶思想 建議大家<br />\n行山嘅時候 個書包入面裝水裝紙巾好喇<br />\n至於你啲身分證 或者其他重要嘢<br />\n有腰包就放腰包（要戴係面衫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">裡面</span></span>啊懵佬）<br />\n無就好似呀婆咁 著條有袋/拉鍊嘅背心底衫喇<br />\n你知啲動物好鍾意咬住個袋唔放 唔俾你走<br />\n只要你個袋無重要嘢 就可以嚟一招<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">金蟬脫殼</span></span>"},{"pid":"7be764f2828eb687a61632223abacaec5c32e551","tid":1506121,"uid":42943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:13:51.000Z","msg":"好似Scott scout 嗰個應該點整？"},{"pid":"165f0e94f0bbff38b11ebf6947f26e68c4b44d89","tid":1506121,"uid":42943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:14:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d828baf1363fda4ee3ed113c693640da64db2870","tid":1506121,"uid":259613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"直接爆左D閘<br />\nD人自然會入架啦"},{"pid":"bc88da687e72f51f4bd44d2ed297989b8dabc2b2","tid":1506121,"uid":30868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:14:50.000Z","msg":"一定要"},{"pid":"e23484e2d8672543c61c717e80e09ca0cbfb24df","tid":1506121,"uid":257447,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:15:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">P牌狗借位，大家覺得有用請幫手開新Post呼籲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">會唔會考慮吓呼籲全世界平日返工放工都跳閘</span><br />\n<br />\n其實「黨鐵」咁樣封半條線，仲要擺明比狗爛運兵車用<br />\n<br />\n會唔會考慮吓呼籲全世界平日返工放工都跳閘<br />\n一兩個人做就會比人搞<br />\n個個都做嘅話點睇？<br />\n文宣會唔會考慮下？<br />\n<br />\n我唔知點先做得起，先講個諗法出嚟<br />\n睇下有冇人做到，呼籲下<br />\n自己人微言輕，唔知點煲大佢<br />\n長者八達通個效果唔明顯<br />\n但跳閘就唔同講法<br />\n又唔洗搵前線打開個閘位，減低前線承受嘅風險，只要肯跳夠多人就做到<br />\n唔單單係星期六日抗爭先做<br />\n係要平日返工放工嘅時候都做<br />\n<br />\n我有呢一個諗法，但唔知點樣煲大佢<br />\n所以先講出嚟睇吓大家有冇D乜嘢諗法</span>"},{"pid":"c0ac8ac7cfd3047197ed8a2cedfd1c229eabcd7a","tid":1506121,"uid":199754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d96695dac52bcfeb5eb3e8e6be86cc381f459091","tid":1506121,"uid":206812,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:13:42.000Z","msg":"家母一路睇電視 見好多人爬山嘅時候<br />\n俾狗咬住個背囊走唔甩 咬到好傷好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以用師奶思想 建議大家<br />\n行山嘅時候 個書包入面裝水裝紙巾好喇<br />\n至於